{"tid":2314161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本、法國、美國明年5月首度聯合軍演","createTime":"2020-12-06T10:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T10:53:47.000Z","uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6505da7a967d129433b8ef25027913557d8588de","tid":2314161,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"中國軍隊在東海和南海加強活動之際，日本、法國、美國明年5月將首度在日本西南方離島舉行陸上、海上聯合軍事演習，以抗衡中國。<br />\n<br />\n中央社引述日本產經新聞報導稱，演習會在日本一座偏遠無人島舉行，將聚焦天災救濟行動，但部分演習內容也構成抵禦攻擊的基礎。<br />\n<br />\n產經新聞未引述消息來源。日本防衛省未立即回覆路透的置評要求。產經新聞提到，這次聯合軍演目的在抗衡中國。中國在東海與日本有領土紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n法國海軍參謀長范迪亞上將（Pierre Vandier）在另一場訪問告訴產經新聞：「我們希望向這個區域展現我方存在，釋出日法合作的訊息。」「這則訊息是針對中國，關乎多邊夥伴關係和航行自由。」<br />\n<br />\n中方曾稱他們在區域內活動是以和平為目的，但日本愈來愈憂心中國海軍在釣魚台列嶼（日本稱尖閣諸島）周邊加強活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201206/23VUTP6P7FDNFIA34KDLEIAGMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201206%2F23VUTP6P7FDNFIA34KDLEIAGMA%2F&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2gPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=d551fac9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201206%2F23VUTP6P7FDNFIA34KDLEIAGMA%2F&h=35d74236\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201206/23VUTP6P7FDNFIA34KDLEIAGMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社：<br />\n<a href=\"https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-japan-france-defence/japan-france-u-s-plan-their-first-joint-military-drills-in-may-media-idUKKBN28G04Y?il=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuk.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fuk-japan-france-defence%2Fjapan-france-u-s-plan-their-first-joint-military-drills-in-may-media-idUKKBN28G04Y%3Fil%3D0&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2gPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=95fd1448\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuk.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fuk-japan-france-defence%2Fjapan-france-u-s-plan-their-first-joint-military-drills-in-may-media-idUKKBN28G04Y%3Fil%3D0&h=a6a02941\" target=\"_blank\">https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-japan-france-defence/japan-france-u-s-plan-their-first-joint-military-drills-in-may-media-idUKKBN28G04Y?il=0</a>"},{"pid":"c226404c8af42ece64e9fd31068f8986828b54fd","tid":2314161,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"打鳩中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db42ae65f5cc4a77f982ab3a07a4190295b38b9","tid":2314161,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"演乜野，邊個買左俄國防衛導彈，就射佢啦"},{"pid":"02278230511566e6b5add612573a0b0d99799017","tid":2314161,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452802a7126e6327a86fea8153b8d229f9991dd3","tid":2314161,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"法國都嚟埋 ?<br />\n<br />\n其實英澳台都玩埋一份啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0386e04f51c33a790554192c5febf3ed590aa2","tid":2314161,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"明年五月演練定實戰？"}]}